---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

import ContactCTA from '../components/ContactCTA.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About | OTTEN Yassir" description="About OTTEN Yassir">
	<div class="stack gap-20">
		<main class="wrapper about">
			<Hero
				title="About"
				tagline="Thanks for stopping by. Read below to learn more about myself and my background."
			>
				<img
					width="1553"
					height="873"
					src="/assets/keyboard.jpeg"
					alt="Jeanine White at work with a colleague"
				/>
			</Hero>

			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Background</h2>
				<div class="content">
   					<p>As a final-year student pursuing a Bachelor's degree in Computer Science, specializing in Networks and Telecommunications at the Higher School of Computer Science (ESI) within the Haute Ecole Bruxelles Brabant (HE2B) group, I am deeply passionate about cybersecurity and cyber defense. With a keen interest in mastering modern technology, I am dedicated to ensuring the integrity and security of digital infrastructure.</p>
    				<p>My skills span across network administration, configuration and security, including expertise with firewalls such as ASA, Juniper, Palo-Alto, and iptables. Additionally, I possess knowledge in management methodologies such as SECinfo and Agile practices. I am enthusiastic about various aspects of cybersecurity, including pentesting, cyber defense, social engineering, and OSINT. Continuously seeking to expand my knowledge, I actively engage with platforms like TryHackMe to stay abreast of industry developments.</p>
    				<p>Looking ahead, I am eager to further my education as a cyber defense engineer, leveraging my academic foundation and practical experience to contribute meaningfully to this critical field. With a proactive approach to learning and a commitment to excellence, I am determined to continue growing and making a lasting impact in the realm of cybersecurity.</p>
				</div>

			</section>
			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Education</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>Bachelor in Computer Science, specializing in Networks and Telecommunications <a href="https://he2b.be/formations/informaticien-reseaux-et-telecommunications/">(ESI HE2B)</a>.</p>
					<p> <a href="https://www.credly.com/badges/046cecdc-cd65-4de4-a9a4-ddfd7d6a1c4d/public_url"> CCNA: Switching, Routing, and Wireless Essentials</a></p>
					<p><a href="https://www.credly.com/badges/82146441-8719-4446-a0ca-600dc587132d/public_url">CISCO: Introduction to Cybersecurity</a></p>
				</div>
			</section>
			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Skills</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>Network : Administration, Windows Server, Cisco Devices, Firewalls, All Linux Distributions, Switching, Routing, Wireless, Virtualisation Environnement and Network Services.</p>
					<p>Developement : Java, JavaFx , C, C++, Js, Php, PL/SQL...</p>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>

		<ContactCTA />
	</div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	.about {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 3.5rem;
	}

	img {
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 1.5rem;
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
	}

	section {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.5rem;
		color: var(--gray-200);
	}

	.section-title {
		grid-column-start: 1;
		font-size: var(--text-xl);
		color: var(--gray-0);
	}

	.content {
		grid-column: 2 / 4;
	}

	.content :global(a) {
		text-decoration: 1px solid underline transparent;
		text-underline-offset: 0.25em;
		transition: text-decoration-color var(--theme-transition);
	}

	.content :global(a:hover),
	.content :global(a:focus) {
		text-decoration-color: currentColor;
	}

	@media (min-width: 50em) {
		.about {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: 1fr 60% 1fr;
		}

		.about > :global(:first-child) {
			grid-column-start: 2;
		}

		section {
			display: contents;
			font-size: var(--text-lg);
		}
	}
</style>
